# HelpSphere tickets-service — .dockerignore (Story 06.5c.1, T8.4)
# Reduz contexto do docker build para o mínimo essencial.

# Build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/

# IDE/editor
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Tests (não vão pra runtime)
tests/

# Docs e config local
**/*.md
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/secrets.json

# Git
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Docker (este próprio arquivo + Dockerfile)
Dockerfile
.dockerignore

# CI
**/.github/
